{"id":232135489,"title":"#7 想說來個看圖就故事","content":"https://i.imgur.com/LMlr2tb.jpg\n\n#想說來個看圖說故事 \n\n這次主題叫「亂」\n上禮拜跟同事在公司附近餐廳午餐。\n都會商業區的窗外難得可以出現這麼接地氣的凌亂電線桿。\n於是借用這個景，我想要重新整理自己。\n把凌亂的線都一條條理乾淨。\n來日本不知不覺四年了，發生了大大小小的事。\n無論是感情、親情、友情。\n時間一久都會慢慢產生一些變化。\n在這四年中，我不斷嘗試著各種不同的事情做。\n可能我也還在漂浮不定的尋找一個定位吧！\n於是首先我打算從紀錄生活開始。\n又開始拍影片了、又開始發些照片日記。\n如此一來也不算是瞎忙吧！\n\n本町、大阪商辦區、午餐激戰場所、其實很多美食都藏在這裡面、但你一定不知道、因為塞滿上班族🤣","excerpt":"#想說來個看圖說故事，這次主題叫「亂」上禮拜跟同事在公司附近餐廳午餐。都會商業區的窗外難得可以出現這麼接地氣的凌亂電線桿。於是借用這個景，我想要重新整理自己。把凌亂的線都一條條理乾淨。來日本不知不覺四","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"ee51d6cd-ad7e-4d73-b79a-3ce32ea7798b","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-09-21T00:33:01.499Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-21T11:10:09.857Z","commentCount":2,"likeCount":10,"tags":[],"topics":["日本生活","想說來個看圖說故事","在大阪的舍監","打工度假","日本工作"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"日本生活","forumAlias":"japan_life","school":"在大阪的舍監momo","department":"chiouehu","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":10}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/LMlr2tb.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"686c3aba-cb4c-4fab-abe0-6cd9dec4905a","url":"https://i.imgur.com/LMlr2tbl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/LMlr2tbl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/LMlr2tbl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-09-21T00:33:01.499Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-21T11:10:09.857Z"},{"id":"686c3aba-cb4c-4fab-abe0-6cd9dec4905a","url":"https://i.imgur.com/LMlr2tb.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/LMlr2tb","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/LMlr2tbl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-09-21T00:33:01.499Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-21T11:10:09.857Z"}],"postAvatar":""}